but also an engineer, scientist,

32
00:01:31,102 --> 00:01:33,915
sculptor, architect, and theorist.

33
00:01:33,915 --> 00:01:36,519
He had knowledge of so many subjects

34
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:38,348
be it painting, cartography,

35
