00:09:38,763 --> 00:09:42,393
So that there are no ill-effects of moisture on this painting,

232
00:09:42,393 --> 00:09:44,853
since it was painted on wood.

233
00:09:44,853 --> 00:09:47,673
So it's necessary to protect it from humidity and moisture.

