00:09:47,673 --> 00:09:49,235
And secondly,

235
00:09:49,235 --> 00:09:51,878
over time, there was bleaching.

236
00:09:51,878 --> 00:09:53,468
Originally, when this was painted,

237
00:09:53,468 --> 00:09:55,755
it used to be more bright and colourful.

