241
00:10:03,734 --> 00:10:05,247
known as Sfumato.

242
00:10:05,247 --> 00:10:07,433
The technique of blending.

243
00:10:07,433 --> 00:10:10,043
The background you see in this painting

244
00:10:10,043 --> 00:10:11,214
is a landscape.

245
00:10:11,214 --> 00:10:12,867
It is the Arno Valley in Italy.

246
00:10:13,248 --> 00:10:17,701
There are no clear boundaries or outlines 
between the background and Mona Lisa.

247
00:10:17,701 --> 00:10:20,734
In some places, Mona Lisa's hair is blended with the landscape.

248
00:10:20,734 --> 00:10:23,328
Blurring the outlines and blending the colours

249
00:10:23,328 --> 00:10:25,267
is the technique of Sfumato.

250
00:10:25,267 --> 00:10:29,165
This is the secret behind Mona Lisa's mysterious smile.

251
00:10:29,165 --> 00:10:31,329
Look at Mona Lisa's smile carefully.

